**Story**
Once upn a time  in a forest, there lived a monkey who resided on a jamoon tree, which was on the banks of a river. In the same forest, there lived a Crocodile and his wife......
The monkey wanted to make a cloth for himself using crocodile skin.He slowly started trying to be friend by feeding him the berries. The berries were delicious and the crocodile liked it. After sometime, the monkey started poisoning the berries....

